Properties.Caption: Просмотр детализации НПА
Properties.Tag: Select [K_ITEM].[CITEM] As [Полномочие], Max([K_ITEM].[NITEM]) As [Наименование полномочия], [K_ITEM_1].[CITEM] As [Вид правового акта], Max([K_ITEM_1].[NITEM]) As [Наименование вида акта], [K_NPA_SPB].[AKT_NMB] As [Номер правового акта], [K_NPA_SPB].[D_SIGN] As [Дата подписания акта], [RO_NPA_DET].[BRubric] As [Абзац НПА], [RO_NPA_DET].[BSubpar] As [Подпункт НПА], [RO_NPA_DET].[BParagr] As [Пункт НПА], [RO_NPA_DET].[BPart] As [Часть НПА], [RO_NPA_DET].[BParticle] As [Статья НПА] From ((([RO_NPA_DET] With (NoLock) Inner Join [K_NPA_SPB] With (NoLock) On ([RO_NPA_DET].[K_NPA_SPBID]=[K_NPA_SPB].[K_NPA_SPBID])) Inner Join [K_ITEM] As [K_ITEM_1] With (NoLock) On ([K_NPA_SPB].[K_ITEMID_VID]=[K_ITEM_1].[K_ITEMID])) Inner Join [K_ITEM] With (NoLock) On ([RO_NPA_DET].[K_ITEMID_PROXY]=[K_ITEM].[K_ITEMID])) Where |0 Group by [K_ITEM].[CITEM], [K_ITEM_1].[CITEM], [K_NPA_SPB].[AKT_NMB], [K_NPA_SPB].[D_SIGN], [RO_NPA_DET].[BRubric], [RO_NPA_DET].[BSubpar], [RO_NPA_DET].[BParagr], [RO_NPA_DET].[BPart], [RO_NPA_DET].[BParticle] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр детализации НПА
